    <p>
      If you have any further questions or if there's anything you'd like more
      information on, please feel free to let me
      <a href="mailto:jared@lettsdev.ca">know</a>.
    </p>

    <p>
      Thank you for your consideration. I look forward to the possibility of
      working together.
    </p>

    <p>
      Best regards,<br />
      Jared Letts<br />
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
